  * Fixed possible crash in displaying particle editor on Linux.
  * Fixed failure to find user-local mod assets in (e.g.) ~/.doom3/darkmod

 -- Matthew Mott <orbweaver3d@gmail.com>  Tue, 29 Nov 2011 19:51:12 +0000

